Class ARISFileCatalog

public class ARISFileCatalog extends GeminiFileCatalog<ARISImageRecord>
File catalog for ARIS sonar files. file format is very simple compared to Tritech files. Details are at https://github.com/SoundMetrics/aris-file-sdk/tree/master
Author:
Doug Gillespie

    • streamCatalog

      public CatalogStreamSummary streamCatalog(CatalogStreamObserver streamObserver) throws CatalogException
      Description copied from class: GeminiFileCatalog
      Start a full forwards only read of the catalog from start to end, sending all records through to the streamObserver.

      Whatever calls this will almost definitely want to do so in a separate worker thread because the call will block until the read has finished.

      Specified by:
